snippet.title: DEATH IN UNISON | Gameplay Reveal
snippet.description:
Survive the world's deadliest psychopaths. Begin your new administration job at a top-secret prison. Test your co-operative skills with a friend or brave the prison alone in an intense survival horror.

Very short look at the gameplay for DEATH IN UNISON. Looking to get a demo out ASAP when ready!

#horrorgaming #indiegame #indiedev #videogames
